item.title: [+1920] Man throws bicycle at thieves
item.description: Two thieves on a motor-scooter flew by and snatched a woman's purse on a street in Wenzhou, China. As he was passing by the front of a hotel near where the thievery happened, he stopped, calmly got off his bicycle, picked it up, and then threw it at the thieves. The bicycle hit them.

item.title: [+464] Men who help clean get more sex
item.description: According to a new study published in the Journal of Family Issues, the more time you spend doing chores, the more often you probably have sex with your partner. In the study, Researchers looked at almost 7,000 married couples and found that people who work hard in one area of their lives tend to work, and play, hard in others.
